      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_C77EED40-2209-0135-E937-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Next to the file you want to delete [1], click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [2] then click the <strong>Delete</strong> link [3]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
